Hi, it's the same version like that befor 2 days, but now can you download it. :)

This is my first surf map called: surf_pinky

It's a hard skill map i think...

It's for tickrate 66, sv_gravity 800 and sv_airaccelerate 150

I made the 5 stages, ente/kopf made the bonus and the jail and AbSoLuTe made the spawn and the bonus ending...

The map timer is 6 minutes. If you end, you got godmode.
